MES 1011 JMH 27/7/09 Interfaces

A User Defined Cam Protocol can have a Query Filter for filtering data further than just the Transaction Types. 

The CMQF_CamTransactionTemplate objects will be created by the system with sufficient query combinations to fulfil 
the JMT to CICS interfaces. More may be added in the future.
</text>
